[ Exhales deeply ]

13:42.055 --> 13:44.624
Aah! [ Groans ]

13:44.657 --> 13:49.229
This is how they
immobilize pigs on farms.

13:49.262 --> 13:50.830
How would you know?

13:50.864 --> 13:54.167
I did a lot of bad things
before I became a hit man.

13:54.201 --> 13:56.336
[ Tie zips ]
[ Groans ]

