hire you to kill me

14:04.677 --> 14:06.846
because you killed him...

14:06.880 --> 14:08.348
and David...

14:08.381 --> 14:10.150
and Silk.

14:10.183 --> 14:12.485
This is all you.

14:12.519 --> 14:14.554
[ Laughing ]

14:14.587 --> 14:17.024
Aah. [ Groans ]

14:17.057 --> 14:18.425
[ Inhales sharply ]

14:19.426 --> 14:29.402
**

14:29.436 --> 14:39.412
**

